{"tid":2423813,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"許志安4月復出｜陪老婆嚴選食材實戰「168斷食」 Sammi親述成效：褲頭鬆咗啲！","createTime":"2021-02-26T06:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T11:14:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"83e56d26acb129ce7568ec8df48b8b3460885547","tid":2423813,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:46:20.000Z","msg":"一向注重自己身型的鄭秀文，平日熱愛做運動keep fit。48歲的她依然保養得宜，最近更正在進行「168飲食法」，Sammi表示:「相信大家都聽過168飲食法，即係你一日廿四小時，有十六小時係唔能夠進食，其餘八小時，就係你可以嘅進食時間喇！」其實「168 斷食法」一早已紅遍全球，連外國女星Jennifer Aniston、台灣女星楊丞琳，都成功減磅。<br />\n<br />\n根據營養師嘅講法，其實「168飲食法」 除了限制飲食時間之外，配合適當食材都相當重要。日前《壹仔》見到Sammi 孖住安仔，親自去超市挑選食材，全程主攻蔬菜、肉類等健康食物。實戰「168飲食法」一個月，Sammi 發現自己意外清減了，而且褲頭仲鬆咗添！她說：「我自己感覺係非常良好，第一就係唔會特別覺得好肚餓。實行起上嚟又唔係想像中咁難，只要一過咗個八個鐘頭，食完夜晚個餐就開始拉鏈口，乜都唔好擺落個口，除咗飲水、黑咖啡、或者茶。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_776977_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_776977_0&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd60PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=f75e76d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_776977_0&h=6031113e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_776977_0</a>"},{"pid":"cab57637db710b9fbee87eb8330dcd11408702ed","tid":2423813,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYiPpYQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYiPpYQ.png&h=2f719a09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1733ae1ff19f4c343372d139c600d7d2cb465d46","tid":2423813,"uid":242537,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:48:17.000Z","msg":"因為安心出痕 apps?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50a370e39d3647001ceac0d91e54fece6f64697","tid":2423813,"uid":242537,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"cab57637db710b9fbee87eb8330dcd11408702ed","tid":2423813,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":22,"scor